# Navigasi Cross-Menu

## Kapan wajib trace multi-menu

- User tanya **proses end-to-end** (order → pick → ship → invoice)
- Fitur di satu menu **memicu efek** di menu lain
- Konsep **bukan satu menu** (Random SKU, consolidation, settlement)
- Test case punya `related_menus`
- README menu menyebut "Menu terkait" / "Used in"

## Sumber trace

| Sumber | Lokasi |
|--------|--------|
| Manifest | `module`, `menu_links`, slug prefix modul |
| README menu | § Menu terkait, Route & code |
| requirement | § integrasi, dependency, downstream |
| technical | Controller/job yang refer menu lain |
| test-cases | `related_menus`, preconditions |
| Konsep khusus | `qa-docs/random-sku/` |

## Pola modul umum

| Alur | Menu contoh (trace via manifest) |
|------|-------------------------------------|
| Fulfillment Omni | sales-order → waves → picking → checking → packing |
| SCM inbound | purchase-requisition → PO → inbound → stock |
| Accounting AR | sales invoice → customer payment → GL/journal |
| Accounting AP | supplier invoice → supplier payment |
| Master data | system-product, variant, BOM → dipakai banyak transaksi |

Daftar di atas **petunjuk trace** — selalu verifikasi slug & requirement di manifest.

## Cara jawab alur lintas menu

1. Gambar **urutan step** (numbered)
2. Sebut **slug + menu_name** tiap langkah
3. Bedakan user action vs system auto
4. Sebut **handoff** antar modul (Omni → SCM → Accounting)
5. Flag gap jika hanya sebagian alur terdokumentasi

## Random SKU

Pertanyaan tentang auto-pick variant, binding marketplace, BOM restriction → baca `random-sku/` dulu, lalu menu spesifik user sebut.
